column2: Form the Chosen of the Old Gods
Call forth warriors to defend the Old Gods faithful.
The Chosen of the Old Gods

The Old Gods of the Reachmen are worshipped in the whole Reach and beyond, but until recently all attempts to unify the faithful were fruitless. [From.GetTitledName] invited the strongest warriors of the Reach, and formed the Chosen of the Old Gods.
Call forth warriors to defend the Hagraven and their followers.

The Hagravens and their cultists had for a long time to stay hidden, in secret shrines and caves. But recently, the worship of these powerful mages and their dark-heart warriors is more spread in the whole Reach, and some of them banded together, calling themselves the Forsworn.
